challengeName: CSFV UI Registration Flow Pages Prototype Update
detailedRequirements:
Task Overview

You are updating the CSFV prototype as outlined below.

Task Requirements

  • Add "Resend Activation Link" link (it will be deadlink) to widget header in Informed-Consent.html page
  • Add same link to Register Form widget header in Registerpage.html page
  • Add new page similar to Informed-Consent.html page :
    • Name : Terms-Of-Use.html
    • Widget header should be 'Terms Of Use'
    • The statment in orange should be : You need to read to the bottom of this terms of use before you can continue
    • Remove 'indiate your page' section.
    • Update the agree buttons statment to : "By clicking "I Agree" below, you agree to the terms of use. If you click "I Do Not Agree" any registration information that you have provided will be deleted."
    • User will have to scroll to bottom of the terms of use in order for buttons to get enabled.

UI Prototype

Provided in challenge forums.

Submission

Updated UI Prototype with notes about what has been changed.
